title: .symmetricDifference()
description: The `.symmetricDifference()` JS method returns a new `Set` object containing elements that are in either the current `Set` object or the `Set` object provided as an argument, but not in both..
content: The method that finds elements that are in either the `Set` object on which it's called or the `Set` object passed as an argument, but not in both, returning a new `Set` with these unique elements.
